  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0baa\u0baf\u0bb5\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b90\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0bc2\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "We will oust President Gotabaya and form an all-party government - United People's Shakti Slurai",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The United People's Power will give full support to the protest against the government on Saturday.",
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa should be removed from office and an all-party government should be formed. JVP rejected our invitation to an all-party government. Member of Parliament Nalin Bandara said that refusal is a problematic issue.",
        "He stated this at a press conference held on Thursday (6) at the office of the Leader of the Opposition in Colombo, while further mentioning that,",
        "Police use tear gas on protesting farmers, similar to bombings in Ukraine.",
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa gets scared when he hears the name Hirunika. We are not carrying out demonstrations for political purposes. Political stability cannot be established without the resignation of Gotabaya Rajapaksa.",
        "Therefore, he should be removed from office and an all-party government should be formed. For this we have called all the parties in the Parliament.",
        "However, JVP Rejected the invitation. We really don't understand what their agenda is. We will extend full support to the demonstration to be carried out on the 9th.",
        "On the 9th, Gotabaya Rajapaksa should be forced to resign. After that, an all-party government acceptable to all should be formed.",
        "Dhammika Perera has been appointed for Bashil Rajapaksa who withdrew from politics due to public protests. Initially, when the popular protests intensified, the Rajapaksa family protected itself by setting up an iron guard called Ranil.",
        "Now that opposition to Ranil has intensified, Bashil is planning to appoint someone else to replace him.",
        "They are afraid to give us a chance because of the fear that if the Sajith Premadasa-led government is formed, a case will surely be filed against the Rajapaksas.",
        "JVP Rejecting the call for an all-party government is problematic. Anurakumara Dissanayake has said that he is ready to accept the post of Prime Minister.",
        "How can he form a government with only 3 MPs? He should realize that the cooperation of other parties is also necessary for that.",
        "A good foundation has now been laid for the formation of an all-party government. He said senior members including United People's Power, Tamil National Federation, members of Parliament who are independent from the government, members who are in the government but do not like the Rajapaksa family, COB committee member Saritha Herath and Sambika Ranawaka are ready to cooperate."
      ],
